{"tid":1977140,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"张建宗真实身份大揭秘！张建宗其实是黄尸？","createTime":"2020-04-17T17:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T23:18:38.000Z","uid":253978,"like":892,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"6eac7ff395b766706e6f3be2f87d4e6d78b658a7","tid":1977140,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eFHy8mY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeFHy8mY.jpg&h=6fc9fa40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n现任香港特别行政区政务司司长张建宗作为香港特别行政区的第二号人物，在过去反修例骚乱中甚少谴责暴徒行为。他暧昧的立场不禁令人怀疑他的真实身份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i5etXiH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi5etXiH.png&h=4e8f80e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在七二一事件发生后，张建宗认为警察的处理手法和市民心目中有很大落差，并认为政府责无旁贷，愿意为事件道歉。香港警察队员佐级协会事后发表声明，认为张建宗的道歉言论不负责任，对张建宗给予最严厉的谴责。作为政府的高级官员，竟然与警队持相反立场，不禁令爱国的市民质疑他是否称职。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhXrJZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhXrJZA.jpg&h=2d831bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在准备区选期间张建宗的言词亦值得大家关注。由七月起的每星期天，在香港各处都有反对派发起的示威活动，几乎全部都会演变成为暴力冲突。在十一月十一日起一连五日的工作天，黑衣暴徒更发起了全港到处堵路阻塞交通的破坏行为 ，声称&ldquo;揽炒&rdquo;香港。而张建宗则在访问中认为一星期后的区选十分重要，希望能够顺利举行。其后香港居然出现了一整个星期的和平，黑衣暴徒的破坏行为完全不见踪影。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HkO21Pv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkO21Pv.png&h=1e54dac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在区选前的一天，张建宗在呼吁示威者让区选顺利举行时，竟然用&ldquo;朋友&rdquo;来称呼示威者。看到这里，大家都几乎知道张建宗是如何看待黄尸示威者了！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4zgLZDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4zgLZDA.png&h=5215e59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n区选的结果更证实了张建宗为何希望区选顺利完成。政府部门一直有收集网上数据以估算区选结果，作为政府内部人员，张建宗很大机会知道市民的投票意向，以及区选的大约结果。如果他确实为了政府着想，他理应放纵黑衣暴徒的破坏行为，以此为延迟或取消区选的理由。但他却多番提出区选必须顺利进行，此行为似乎在帮助反对派取得优势。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ug7rJ4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUg7rJ4X.jpg&h=3fef1753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n综合以上分析，张建宗确实为一只不折不扣的黄尸，收着政府的薪酬，却和政府、警队打对台，站在黄尸的一边。香港政府应尽早取缔这个卖国黄尸，并聘用一个真真正正爱国爱港的政务司司长。"},{"pid":"e1d0bb41765f7b87bf00eab1ff1fb4d9ec0890ee","tid":1977140,"uid":253978,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【鬥黃】邊個夠黃同我入嚟簽晒啲聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972114</a>"},{"pid":"6966f9ac1031053fedb2adb05fdfa3ea1a1474c5","tid":1977140,"uid":305553,"like":133,"dislike":3,"score":130,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:42:50.000Z","msg":"宗仔手足嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b85d68b2a4ace6f5cf70bd36abec401195bb8d1","tid":1977140,"uid":189109,"like":102,"dislike":2,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:43:07.000Z","msg":"張建宗係偽藍真黃屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd86c39cf5fe3a051196202ddf7ae9c3ff44351","tid":1977140,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf3dc866562bf19b929247adc5f90479932b05e","tid":1977140,"uid":3465,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTim